          <span class="ba-label">#5 · $39–59/MO · LOCAL SEO SPECIALIST</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">BrightLocal — Best for agencies with local service business clients</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For agencies managing restaurants, HVAC companies, dentists, and other local businesses that live and die by Map Pack rankings.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">BrightLocal is the standard tool for local SEO agencies. Its Local Search Grid shows ranking positions for every client keyword on a geographic map — essential for multi-location businesses. White-label branded reports in the local SEO format clients actually understand. Citation management across 80+ directories. Review monitoring across Google, Yelp, and Facebook. At $39–59/month (not per client, per account), BrightLocal's economics work well for agencies: one account manages unlimited client locations with per-location pricing only on certain features.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Local Search Grid — geo-grid Map Pack rank tracking for every client</h4><p>Show clients exactly where they rank in Google Maps across their service area. The visualization alone justifies the tool in client presentations.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>White-label local SEO reports — the format local business clients actually understand</h4><p>Local business clients don't care about DA or backlink velocity. They care about ranking for "plumber near me." BrightLocal's reports speak their language.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Citation management and review monitoring across 80+ directories</h4><p>Covers the citation and reputation layer of local SEO that national SEO tools ignore.</p></div></li>
