        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">AgencyAnalytics is purpose-built for one job: making clients happy with beautiful, branded reporting. Unlimited campaigns. Full white-label — custom domain, your logo and colors, automated monthly report emails, client login portals with your branding. The integrations are extensive: Google Analytics, Search Console, Ahrefs, Semrush, Facebook Ads, Google Ads, and 80+ more. At $12–18 per client per month, it's the most cost-effective way to give every client a premium-feeling dashboard at an agency price point.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Best white-label client experience in this list — fully branded portals</h4><p>Custom domain, your logo on every report, automated email delivery, client login with your branding. Clients believe it's your proprietary platform.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>80+ integrations — pull all client data into one dashboard</h4><p>Google Analytics, Search Console, Ahrefs, Semrush, all ad platforms. Everything the client cares about in one branded view.</p></div></li>
