        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Surfer SEO scores content against top-ranking competitors in real time. As your writer drafts an article, Surfer shows the content score, keyword density, NLP entity coverage, and recommended word count. For agencies running content teams, it's the quality-control layer that ensures every article meets on-page standards before publishing. Team access and API access on higher plans allow workflow integration into your content production pipeline.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
